                        <interp inst="t18350921-name-850" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD STOCKBRIDGE</persName>
                  </hi>. I have no animosity against him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Jury. Q.</hi> Where were the slippers? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Near his bed-side—I slept next the wall—the trowsers were on the fender, on the other side of the room.</p>
